dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Calumet_Addresses_2017.gdb.[Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.calumetmaps.com/data.htmlThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
